Package com.flipfit.bean

Class GymCenter

java.lang.Object
com.flipfit.bean.GymCenter
public class GymCenter extends Object
Represents a gym center within the FlipFit system. This class stores details about a gym, including its owner, location, capacity, and verification status.
Author:
Dhruv

      address - The physical address of the gym.
      slotCount - The total number of available time slots per day.
      seatsPerSlotCount - The number of seats or capacity for each slot.
      isVerified - The verification status of the gym.
